 F$ 到 $B C ， C D$ 距离为 0.4 ，有个圆形通道经过 $E ， F$ ，且与 $A D$ 只有一个交点，求圆形通道的周长 $\\qquad$ . (精确到 $0.01)$\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-118.jpg?height=318&width=304&top__y=889&top__x=299","line":2324},{"title":"|401x429","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-161.jpg?height=429&width=401&top__y=982&top__x=468","line":3169,"embedded":true},{"title":"50,60$ ) 内的人数为 16 ，则下列结论正确的是（）\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-185.jpg?height=435&width=618&top__y=1781&top__x=296","line":3666}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"19gd1oy","at":1771470843325}},"smart_blocks:20-Product/01-数学教学/讲义/09-讲义汇总/XDF讲义/FY25 高三数学秋季【行远班教材】3.0.md#目录": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.04270237,-0.00766747,0.07654399,-0.01820724,0.02356493,-0.00347283,-0.06036055,0.06011983,0.02303573,0.0362582,0.02413705,-0.08089932,0.04114982,0.006614,0.00365971,-0.02431194,0.04770277,-0.03433792,-0.05515104,-0.02154933,0.13009085,-0.01550038,-0.0134204,-0.0442882,0.09258578,0.04712398,0.00065465,-0.05646965,-0.02615798,-0.19046782,-0.00642124,0.0663358,0.06779701,0.03667082,0.04100715,-0.04555472,-0.02654921,0.04964275,-0.01109597,0.03452746,0.00091225,0.08535534,-0.00900476,-0.00059842,0.00993117,-0.08335643,-0.0618713,-0.03175468,0.03799658,-0.00839362,-0.04509782,-0.02346433,0.00925322,0.03493287,-0.05531339,0.00907905,0.03054178,0.02032559,0.01280191,0.03904383,0.0244448,-0.00531693,-0.21516368,0.04049027,0.05250473,-0.02128236,-0.02833437,-0.04404546,0.02145085,0.09357114,-0.02419147,-0.0158742,-0.01431605,0.00794761,-0.00821743,-0.01937286,-0.00001339,-0.09564626,-0.01970005,-0.0720145,-0.01954375,0.09035622,-0.03101919,0.00729696,0.00495834,0.04084475,0.00005962,-0.05590978,0.01468488,-0.05815474,0.00494585,-0.02648094,-0.01454602,0.00795516,-0.07275633,-0.0429015,0.02365861,0.02399778,-0.02479537,0.08771592,-0.04140131,0.0